    Mass Spell Destruction: by 4 + (Abj foci * 2) max 14
    Nature's Frailty: by 11 + (Abj foci * 3) max 26
    Breach Balls: by 7
    Persuade: by a (stacking) max of 6 for 5 rounds
    If there is no difference between min and max values either no one lowered SR or you are only logging already lowered SRs
